snippet.title: SpiderHeck - Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Spiders with laser swords is finally available for PS4 & PS5!

SpiderHeck is a fast-paced couch co-op brawler where spiders dance to the death in the grip of chaotic battles using laser swords while evading certain doom with strategic web shooting.

#ps5games #ps5 #ps4games #ps4
